                  "blocks": {
                    "text_mkw4eC": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>Cover has undergone a structured programme of real-world and controlled impact testing, designed to reflect the conditions cricketers actually face.</p><p>Testing has included:</p><ul><li>High-velocity impact testing using cricket balls at representative match speeds</li><li>Repeated strike testing to assess structural integrity over time</li><li>Extended wear testing during training sessions and competitive match play</li><li>On-field validation across batting, wicket-keeping, bowling and close-in fielding positions</li></ul><p>This programme allowed us to refine the shell construction, internal energy-absorbing layers, shape and stability — delivering consistent protection without unnecessary bulk.</p>",
                        "width": "100%",
                        "max_width": "normal",
                        "alignment": "left",
                        "type_preset": "custom",
                        "font": "var(--font-body--family)",
