                  "blocks": {
                    "text_pN97a9": {
                      "type": "text",
                      "settings": {
                        "text": "<p>Core Cover must be worn inside a jock strap or compression shorts with a dedicated pouch. It should sit snugly, centred and securely positioned before play begins. We recommend purchasing the bundle so that your Core Cover works with our Jockstrap as they are designed to work together as a system.</p>",
